name: Wonderful 2-bd apart with balcony. Plaza Cataluña
description:
The Collection Barcelona welcomes you to this comfortable 2-bedroom apartment located next to Plaza Catalunya, the heart of Barcelona.

The apartment can accommodate up to 4 guests, with a living area that features a relaxing sofa and a flat screen TV, dining area, and fully-equipped kitchen with all the appliances. This apartment has a great balcony ideal to enjoy Barcelona's summer days.

The apartment is 3 minutes from Metro Plaza de Catalunya (Red Line L1 & Green Line L3).
host_about:
Hey! Adam here! I love welcoming guests from all over the world to stay and enjoy the city where I was born and raised. Explore Barcelona from one of my amazingly located apartments, enjoy the sights, the Spanish-Catalan atmosphere and immerse on a local experience during your holidays.  

I am working together with a professional team of people managing the apartments, available 24/7 during your stay and with the same focus on personal and attentive services. All my apartments are in Eixample district, an ideal spot for culture and gastronomy lovers, the perfect area to explore the city and enjoy from the catalan atmosphere. 

Looking forward to host you :)
